---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Prathamesh Mishra"
  description="Privacy policy for prathamesh.dev — what data is collected and how it is used."
>
  <main style="padding-top: 80px; padding-bottom: 96px;">
    <div class="container privacy-page">

      <div class="privacy-header reveal">
        <span class="section-label">Privacy</span>
        <h1 class="privacy-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="privacy-meta mono">Last updated: June 2026</p>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-body reveal" style="--delay: 80ms;">

        <section class="privacy-section">
          <h2>What this site collects</h2>
          <p>
            This site does not use analytics software, tracking pixels, cookies, or any
            other form of site monitoring. No data about your browsing behaviour is
            collected or stored by this site.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-section">
          <h2>Contact form</h2>
          <p>
            When you submit the contact form, the information you provide — your name,
            email address, and message — is sent to and processed by
            <strong>Formspree</strong> (formspree.io), a third-party form handling
            service. This data is used only to respond to your enquiry. It is not shared
            with any other party and is never sold.
          </p>
          <p>
            Formspree retains form submissions for 30 days by default. You can request
            deletion of your data at any time by emailing
            <a href="mailto:mprathamesh2023@gmail.com">mprathamesh2023@gmail.com</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-section">
          <h2>Third-party services</h2>
          <p>
            The only third-party service this site sends data to is Formspree, and only
            when you actively submit the contact form. Formspree's own privacy policy is
            available at formspree.io/legal/privacy-policy.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-section">
          <h2>Your rights (UK GDPR)</h2>
          <p>
            Under UK GDPR you have the right to access, correct, or request deletion of
            any personal data held about you. To exercise any of these rights, or if you
            have a question about how your data is handled, contact:
          </p>
          <div class="privacy-contact">
            <a href="mailto:mprathamesh2023@gmail.com" class="privacy-email">
              mprathamesh2023@gmail.com
            </a>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-section">
          <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
          <p>
            If this policy changes, the updated version will be posted at this URL with
            a revised date at the top.
          </p>
        </section>

        <div class="privacy-back">
          <a href="/" class="back-link mono">← Back to portfolio</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .privacy-page {
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .privacy-header {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .privacy-title {
    font-size: var(--step-3);
    margin-top: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .privacy-meta {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--text-lo);
  }

  .privacy-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .privacy-section h2 {
    font-size: var(--step-1);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--text-hi);
  }

  .privacy-section p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .privacy-section p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .privacy-section a {
    color: var(--signal);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .privacy-contact {
    margin-top: 12px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    background: var(--ink-800);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 2px;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .privacy-email {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--signal);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .privacy-email:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .privacy-back {
    padding-top: 16px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .back-link {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text-lo);
    transition: color 200ms;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    color: var(--text-hi);
  }
</style>
